oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: "Turkey Toe" Smith
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Photograph of a man known as "Turkey Toe" Smith sitting on Main Street in Crossville. John Wesley "Turkey Toe" Smith (1872-1952) taught singing and was a layman in the Methodist church.
